💛 Empathy builds strong, resilient teams! 
👉 Tip: Understand the personal and professional challenges your team members face. Empathy fosters connection and better collaboration.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
